WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:13.400
The Fully Automatic Horizontal Baler is the most technology advanced and experience condensed product from SINOBALER.

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:22.100
It can achieve a continuous automatic baling of cardboard, paper, carton boxes, natural fiber, packing material, etc.

00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:36.500
An in-feed conveyor can be connected for continuous 
material feeding to increase efficiency,

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:43.800
as the conveyor is fully automatic and can auto start and stop according to the amount of material in the hopper.

00:00:43.860 --> 00:00:49.000
Besides conveyor, you can also choose other feeding device such as cyclone system.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:12.100
De-jamming cylinders can easily push down any jammed material 
at the feeding mouth into the chamber,

00:01:12.100 --> 00:01:15.100
enabling the ram push through successfully.

00:01:15.100 --> 00:01:40.200
With this baler, the feeding, compressing, wire threading, wire twisting, tying, wire cutting and bale ejection are all done automatically.

00:01:40.200 --> 00:02:00.600
It compresses loose materials into dense, regularly shaped bales, greatly facilitating your storage space and transportation cost.

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:10.000
Technical support is provided throughout machines' entire lifespan.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:13.900
This color touchscreen panel features a clear, 
easy to understand interface.

00:02:13.900 --> 00:02:20.000
It allows for simple machine operation, parameter setting and even advanced troubleshooting.

00:02:23.600 --> 00:02:26.100
These tension cylinders at the bale exit opening give bales one last press before pushing it out to ensure bales are neat and dense.

00:02:34.100 --> 00:02:40.600
On-site support can be arranged for machine installation.

00:02:40.600 --> 00:02:50.000
Our engineers can also set aside time to provide on-site training to your operators,

00:02:50.000 --> 00:03:00.000
demonstrate proper troubleshooting and maintenance procedures

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:20.000
